				<td colspan="2"><span>I agree in general that the AE songs don't have much use. I have used the AE slow, however, in a couple of circumstances. For example, on LDONS if folks are well geared it is faster to just AE slow the 2 to 4 mobs and then kill them. The same is true if you have to help someone in one of the POJ trials. There are a few uses for it, but they are situational only. And to my understanding--please correct me if I am wrong--mobs slowed with the AE slow stay slowed for the three ticks the song stays on them even if the dot component doesn't do any damage because the mobs are moving.
