<br />
AE groups:
<br />

<br />
AE raids: PoEearth Mud Ring, Coirnav, PoAir Dust, often in Akheva (train to boss and AE the train)
<br />

<br />
AE'ing the greenies:
<br />

<br />
AE Slow: Sometimes in a new situation, it is very useful to have the no dmg AE slow (Largo's) because you dont know how many mobs you may have to deal with and having it memmed is a good coverall for many emergency situations.
<br />

<br />
FUN: I love it,  take Zuriki's for example.  I do 191 / tick with Lute of the Flowing Waters.  For 10 mobs that is 1910 / tick = 318 DPS from one song alone.  If you are lucky to get more than 10 and you sing 4 AE sings your DPS is greater than any class in game.  Don't get to say that very often =)
<br />

<br />
AE songs are situational, BUT in those situations they utterly rock.
<br />

